description: This file is the entry point for a React web application. It imports React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component, then renders the App into the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the React component tree into the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree under the created root.
